CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 26, 1953, page 7, reads: "Ushers Alliance Gives Christmas Baskets - Pictured above are members of the Ushers Alliance which handled Christmas baskets at Wesley Center AME Zion Church, Tuesday, Dec. 22, Charles Daniels, president: E. Miller, T. Jamison, G. Lawley, C. Williams, M. Thomas, M. Lucas, J. H. Jones, S. Cobbs, M. Jemison, C. Sweed, C. Daniels, C. Winkfield, R. Washington, H. Weaver, W. Cooper, G. Jones, S. Barron, G. Winkfield and C. Brown. Articles by the sewing project committee were given to the hospitals. John H. Jones is chairman of the social commitee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of the Ushers Alliance, including: E. Miller, T. Jamison, G. Lawley, C. Williams, M. Thomas, M. Lucas, John H. Jones, S. Cobbs, M. Jemison, C. Sweed, Charles Daniels, C. Winkfield, R. Washington, H. Weaver, W. Cooper, G. Jones, S. Barron, G. Winkfield, and C. Brown, standing behind table of Christmas baskets, another version
